1
00:00:01,415 --> 00:00:20,391
Vodan puje mi.

2
00:00:20,411 --> 00:00:20,692
Daman puje mi.

3
00:00:20,711 --> 00:00:24,199
Sangam puje mi.

4
00:00:30,018 --> 00:00:58,810
Namo tassa bhagavato harahato sambha sambhu dasa Namo tassa bhagavato harahato sambha sambhu dasa Namo tassa bhagavato harahato sambha sambhu dasa

5
00:01:00,021 --> 00:01:23,969
Iti piso bhagava arahamsambhasambhodo vijacaranasampanno sugato lokavidu anuttaro purisadam sarati sata deva manusanam bodho bhagavati

6
00:01:24,861 --> 00:01:49,435
Je čá Buda a títá čá, je čá Buda a nága tá, pachupáná čá je Buda a hangvandámi sápadá, náty mé sáranán ganyán, buddho mé sáranán gwarán, eténa sácha vajé ná, hotu mé čá já mangalán,

7
00:01:50,292 --> 00:02:16,219
kájéna váčá čiténa, pámádéna majákatán, hačéán kámámé bánté, bůrý páňá tatágatán.

8
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,122
Svákáto bhagavatá dámo, sánditíko akáliko, hejí pásíko opanájíko, pachátán veditá bovinjuhíti.

9
00:02:18,962 --> 00:02:40,698
Ye ca dhamma ati taca, ye ca dhamma anagata, pachupang na ca ye dhamma aham vandami sabbata.

10
00:02:40,717 --> 00:02:42,860
Nati me saranam ganyam, tambo me saranam varam, etena sacca vajena, hotu me jaya mangalam.

11
00:02:43,819 --> 00:03:08,072
kajena vachachitena pamadena mayakatam achyam khammedhamma sandhitika akalika supatipanno bhagavato savakasangho ujupatipanno bhagavato savakasangho

12
00:03:08,828 --> 00:03:22,425
Nyāyāpatipanno bhagavato sāvakasangho, samicchipatipanno bhagavato sāvakasangho.

13
00:03:22,444 --> 00:03:34,060
Yadidhāñcatāri puri sāyugāni atta puri sāpukalā, hesa bhagavato sāvakasangho.

14
00:03:34,764 --> 00:03:48,563
Ahunejo, pahunejo, dakinejo, anjalikaraniyo, anuttarang, punyakedang, lokasati.

15
00:03:48,584 --> 00:03:59,658
Jejasanga, atitacha, jejasanga, anagadam, pachupanacha, yesanga, ahanguandam, isapadam.

16
00:04:00,466 --> 00:04:24,870
Nati me saranam ganyam, sangome saranam varam, etena sacca vajena, hutume jaya mangalam, kajena vachacitena, pamadena mayakatam, acciam kamame sanga, punyaketam ganuttaram.

17
00:04:29,812 --> 00:04:55,379
Aneka jati sansarang, sanda vysangang ibisang, gahakaraka gawe santo, duka jati punapunang, gahakaraka detozi, punagehang nakahazi, sabate pasukabhaga, gahakutang visangatang.

18
00:04:56,086 --> 00:05:09,625
Vysankaragatanchitam tananam kaya macchagam.

19
00:05:09,646 --> 00:05:12,410
Avijapachya sankara sankara pachya vijnanam.

20
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:19,100
Vijnanam pachya namarupam namarupapachya salayatanam.

21
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,963
Salayatanapachya pasopasapachya vedanam.

22
00:05:21,718 --> 00:05:50,713
vedana pachyá tanhá tanhá pachyá upádaná upádaná pachyá bhavá bhavá pachyá jati jati pachyá jará bhádaná soká paridevá duká domanás upáyásá sambhá vanti he vangetásá kevalásá duká kandásá samudá johoti

23
00:05:52,194 --> 00:06:02,889
A vijajá tvevá asézá, viragá nirodá, sankhára nirodá.

24
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:09,920
Sankhára nirodá, vijnána nirodá.

25
00:06:10,641 --> 00:06:14,446
Vijnána nirodá, námá rupá nirodá.

26
00:06:14,466 --> 00:06:18,050
Námá rupá nirodá, sála jatná nirodá.

27
00:06:18,723 --> 00:06:47,024
salajatana nirodha pasa nirodho pasa nirodha vedana nirodho vedana nirodha tanna nirodho tanna nirodha upadana nirodho upadana nirodho bhava nirodho bhava nirodho jati nirodho

28
00:06:47,680 --> 00:07:06,009
Jati nirodha, jara, marana, sukha, parideva, dukkha, domna, supaya, sani, rujanti, hevange, tasa, kevalasa, dukkha, kandasa, nirodho, hoti.

29
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:24,817
Sabe sankhara nityati, yad apanyaya pasati, atane bindati duke, esamago vissudhyam.

30
00:07:24,838 --> 00:07:33,447
Sabe sankhara dukati, yad apanyaya pasati, atane bindati duke, esamago vissudhyam.

31
00:07:34,406 --> 00:07:57,783
Sabe dama anatati, yad apanya yapasati, atani bindati duke, esamago visudhya.

32
00:07:57,802 --> 00:07:59,384
Anicca vata sankhara, upadavaya damino, upajitva nirujanti, tezang upasamosuko.

33
00:08:00,175 --> 00:08:22,730
Dukhavata sankhara upadvajadamino upajitva nirujanti tezang upasamosukho.

34
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:25,254
Anatavata sankhara upadvajadamino upajitva nirujanti tezang upasamosukho.

35
00:08:28,762 --> 00:08:43,041
Imájá dámánu dámá pati pati já bodhám pujéni.

36
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:50,331
Imájá dámánu dámá pati pati já dámám pujéni.

37
00:08:57,567 --> 00:09:04,927
Imájá dámánu dámá páté páté já sáňkám půjémí.

